high_descs: Turn left and go around the island to the other side.
Pick up the gray knife towards the edge
Turn right and then left to go around the island to the sink on the other side.
Place the gray knife in the sink.
Wash everything in the sink with running water and pick up the gray knife again.
Move over to the right of the sink and place the gray knife in the top drawer on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed knife in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward. Turn to the left and walk to the island. Turn right to face it.
Pick up the knife off of the island.
Turn right and go forward. Step to the left and then go forward to the sink.
Place the knife inside the sink. Turn on the water and then take the knife out.
Turn around then open the drawer that is to the right of the sink.
Place the knife inside the drawer and shut it.
anns.task_desc: Wash a knife then place in drawer.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the left end of the island where there is a knife
Pick up the knife from the island
Walk to the sink on in front of the window across from the other end of the island
Place the knife on the handle of the spoon inside the sink, turn the faucet on to fill the sink with water to wash the knife, drain the sink, pick up the knife
Turn and walk to the silverware drawer to the right of the sink
Open the drawer, place the knife in the right side of the drawer, close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Pick up the knife from the island, wash the knife, place it in the silverware drawer
